                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291029-241-off1361 t18291029-241-cd1362"></join>, 1 saw, value 6s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18291029-241-victim1944" type="victimName">
                     William 
