                     <interp inst="t18291029-241-verdict1364" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 25.</p>
               <p>Recommended to Mercy by the Jury - <rs id="t18291029-241-punish1365" type="punishmentDescription">
